## PROJECT STRUCTURE

```
supabase/
├── migrations/           # Postgres schema, RLS — see supabase-postgres.mdc
└── functions/            # Edge Functions (Deno) — see supabase-edge-functions.mdc

src/
├── modules/              # Feature modules (route-based grouping)
│   └── [feature]/
│       ├── components/   # Feature-specific components
│       ├── hooks/        # Feature-specific hooks (often wrap React Query)
│       ├── api/          # React Query queries & mutations (call services — no raw client in UI)
│       ├── store/        # Zustand slices (if needed)
│       ├── types.ts      # Feature types
│       └── index.ts      # Public exports
├── components/           # Shared/common UI components
│   └── ui/               # shadcn/ui generated components (do not edit manually)
├── hooks/                # Shared custom hooks
├── services/             # Supabase (and other backend) facades — single place for .from(), .rpc(), Edge Function fetch
├── lib/                  # Utilities, helpers, constants (e.g. createBrowserClient wrapper if not in services)
├── generated/            # Orval output for optional OpenAPI clients; Supabase DB types if generated here
├── router/               # React Router route definitions
│   └── index.tsx
├── types/                # Global TypeScript types
└── App.tsx
```

- Group by **feature/route**, not by file type (no flat `/components`, `/hooks` at root without the structure above)
- Common components used across features live in `src/components/`
- Co-locate tests next to the file they test: `Component.test.tsx`

